    {
      "id": "WL1",
      "text": [
        "Wind scrapes the world down to bone. Somewhere ahead, a door hangs open like a dare.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "Placeholder Demo: This file exists so the story loads from the library. Item use/equip works." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "WL1A", "text": "Enter the ruined store.", "to": "WL2" },
        { "id": "WL1B", "text": "Check your gear first.", "to": "WL3" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "WL2",
      "text": [
        "Inside: dust, shadows, and a soft clicking sound you can’t place.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "hint", "text": "If your HP is low, try using Bandage or Clean Water from Inventory." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "WL2A", "text": "Move slowly. Listen.", "to": "WL4" },
        { "id": "WL2B", "text": "Move fast. Grab anything useful.", "to": "WL5" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "WL3",
      "text": [
        "Your hands check familiar shapes: a Machete, a Scrap Vest, and the Flashlight’s cold grip."
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "WL3A", "text": "Go in.", "to": "WL2" },
        { "id": "WL3B", "text": "Return to Main Menu.", "to": "MENU" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "WL4",
      "text": [
        "In the back aisle you find a torn page: a Map Fragment.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "You gain: Map Fragment." }
      ],
      "choices": [
        { "id": "WL4A", "text": "Pocket it and leave.", "to": "WL6" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "WL5",
      "text": [
        "A board snaps. Pain lances your foot.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "HP -1 (placeholder consequence)." }
      ],
      "effects": { "resourcesDelta": { "HP": -1 } },
      "choices": [
        { "id": "WL5A", "text": "Keep going anyway.", "to": "WL6" },
        { "id": "WL5B", "text": "Stop and treat it (use Bandage).", "to": "WL6" }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "WL6",
      "text": [
        "Outside again, the sky is the same color as old bruises.",
        { "__sys": true, "tier": "neutral", "text": "Placeholder ending. Full Wasteland comes next." }
      ],
